name: Payton Martin
text: I love Italian Pie! I have been coming here since I was a kid and couldn't see over the counter. Staff is always friendly and the food is always amazing. The staff knows my order, so when I walk in, they bring me my drinks and my food is â€¦More

name: Carolyn Ricapito
text: I have eaten here many times for lunch and always enjoyed the very fresh Mediterranean salad with delicious tomato basil dressing and the whole wheat crust  pizza.  It makes a perfect lunch.   There are many other good choices: Eggplant sandwich, veggie sandwich, chicken.  Good service and pleasant atmosphere.

name: Myrwyn
text: Love eating here, the pasta an Calzones are made to order. My favorite is Seafood Ravioli pasta w/ garlic bread. The service is excellent and the servers are attentive.

name: Blake Leger
text: Decent service. Decent food. I got the shrimp fettucine Alfredo which was okay but tasted bland. I'd probably eat here again.

name: Mike Smith
text: Great taste, quality and quantity and friendly service for your buck.  Definitely beats eating a sub from somewhere.

name: Robert Whiting
text: Great food, good, service, reasonable prices

name: Maggie Webster
text: Food is good, but they never answer the phone.

name: John Tooraen
text: Ownership changed.... food quality down. I won't go back.

name: Arun Nayar
text: A good selection of Italian delicacies at reasonable prices

name: Joseph Taboada
text: Great food, quiet atmosphere, love it!
